properties.areaDesc: Eastern Strait of Juan de Fuca
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 15 at 3:10AM PST until January 15 at 10:00PM PST by NWS Seattle WA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southeast winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Eastern Strait of Juan de Fuca.

* WHEN...From 1 PM this afternoon to 10 PM PST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 1 PM THIS AFTERNOON TO 10 PM PST THIS EVENING
